  Privacy notice
</h1>


<p class="govuk-body">The Apply for Healthy Start service is operated by the Department of Health and Social Care (DHSC).</p>

<p class="govuk-body">DHSC is the data controller of your personal data (information). A data controller determines how and why data is processed.
  We need to process your data to operate the Apply for Healthy Start service.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">
  You can read the <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/organisations/department-of-health-and-social-care/about/personal-information-charter" target="_blank">
  DHSC personal data charter</a> for more information.</p>

<p class="govuk-body">Our cookie notice explains how our service will interact with your device.</p>

